A table of sections codes and official names associated to products

ots_sections_names.Rd

Provides section names from the Harmonized System.

ots_sections_names

Format

A data frame with 2 observations on the following 2 variables.

section_code

Section code (e.g. 01)

section_fullname_english

Section name (e.g. Live Animals; Animal Products)

Examples

ots_sections_names
#>     section_code
#>  1:           01
#>  2:           02
#>  3:           03
#>  4:           04
#>  5:           05
#>  6:           06
#>  7:           07
#>  8:           08
#>  9:           09
#> 10:           10
#> 11:           11
#> 12:           12
#> 13:           13
#> 14:           14
#> 15:           15
#> 16:           16
#> 17:           17
#> 18:           18
#> 19:           19
#> 20:           20
#> 21:           21
#> 22:           22
